body.p:
I respectfully ask to substitute the services of the bearer Walter Godey, in the office, 
        for the present, instead of my own—having made an arrangement with him to that effect, 
        if permitted by you. He writes a good hand, and I think would soon get broke in, 
        and prove efficient. I would ask you to put him at my desk and give him a trial—on some letters first, before giving him the books—(or any other work or arrangement thought best.)
